        &lt;div class=&quot;text-center&quot;&gt;
            &lt;h4&gt;My Contributions&lt;/h4&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;

        &lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-5 col-sm-offset-1&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;ul class=&quot;list&quot;&gt;
                        &lt;li&gt;Candy Surprise.&lt;/li&gt;
                        &lt;span class=&quot;li-span&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;Reworked the experience of opening a candy surprise from flow, visuals, and interactions. - Candy Surprise is the main driver for our collection system. It's a box that contains stickers that you need to unlock charcters and boosters.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

                        &lt;li&gt;Live Ops.&lt;/li&gt;
                        &lt;span&gt;&lt;i&gt;Worked on creating and organizing Bubblegum troll event which was running through the summer of 2019. The event was a team event and was active for only a limited amount of time and the reward was the Bubblegum troll character. The players that played even further after unlocking the character also got a skin for him.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

                        
                        
                    &lt;/ul&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;

         &lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-5 col-sm-offset-0&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;ul class=&quot;list&quot;&gt;
                        &lt;li&gt;Quest System.&lt;/li&gt;
                        &lt;span&gt;&lt;i&gt;Parsing for reading and saving quests and introduction tutorial.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

                        &lt;li&gt;Pre Game Screen.&lt;/li&gt;
                        &lt;span&gt;&lt;i&gt;Reworked the pre game screen with better visuals and to showcase all the available characters for the level and the ability to hotswap between their respective outfits.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

                        
                    &lt;/ul&gt;
